ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectProtocol to the 1979 Convention on Long-range Transboundary Air Pollution to Abate Acidification, Eutrophication and Ground-level Ozone and the Amendment of the text of and annexes II to IX to the 1999 Protocol to Abate Acidification, Eutrophication and Ground-level Ozone and the addition of new annexes X and XI
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to take the actions necessary to BRING INTO FORCE for Canada, the Protocol to the 1979 Convention on Long-range Transboundary Air Pollution to Abate Acidification, Eutrophication and Ground-level Ozone, adopted at Gothenburg on 30 November 1999 and the Amendment of the text of and annexes II to IX to the 1999 Protocol to Abate Acidification, Eutrophication and Ground-level Ozone and the addition of new annexes X and XI, adopted at Geneva on May 4, 2012.
